    <item>
      <title>在特朗普的第二次中期选举中，民主党正在寻找斗士</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/us/politics/democrats-midterms-trump-mood-fighters.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党人表示，党内的态度已经发生转变，对发誓要彻底改革体制的外部候选人的胃口越来越大。一些人担心这一趋势在 11 月份可能会付出高昂的代价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/us/politics/democrats-midterms-trump-mood-fighters.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 09:01:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对北约态度冷淡，土耳其主办峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/world/middleeast/nato-summit-turkey-erdogan-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着特朗普总统对这一联盟态度冷淡，其成员将土耳其庞大的军队和充满活力的国防部门视为资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/world/middleeast/nato-summit-turkey-erdogan-trump.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 09:01:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其外长表示，埃尔多安与特朗普的友谊可以帮助北约</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/world/europe/nato-turkey-erdogan-trump-hakan-fidan.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其最高外交官哈坎·菲丹在接受采访时表示，雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安总统和特朗普总统之间的关系可以缓解北约紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/world/europe/nato-turkey-erdogan-trump-hakan-fidan.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 09:01:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃米尔·博夫在法庭上为特朗普辩护。然后特朗普任命他为法官。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/us/emil-bove-judge-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统正在任命他的前私人律师担任法官，这是他在联邦法院打上烙印的更大努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/us/emil-bove-judge-trump.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 09:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约峰会前夕，俄罗斯致命袭击基辅岩石</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/05/world/europe/kyiv-ukraine-russia-attack-nato.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯在不到一周内发动了第二次重大袭击，弹道导弹袭击了乌克兰首都。官员称，至少有12人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/05/world/europe/kyiv-ukraine-russia-attack-nato.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 08:36:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求国际足联审查美国球员的停赛决定。现在他有资格参加比赛了。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/05/us/trump-fifa-balogun-world-cup.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗拉林·巴洛贡世界杯禁赛的逆转是非常不寻常的。这是自1962年以来国际足联首次取消世界杯期间吃到红牌的禁赛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/05/us/trump-fifa-balogun-world-cup.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 06:57:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普如何将自己置于美国 250 周年的中间</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/05/us/politics/trump-america-250th-anniversary.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[批评者称，总统将自己的形象和举措放在首位，模糊了对国家的忠诚和对他自己的忠诚之间的界限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/05/us/politics/trump-america-250th-anniversary.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 00:52:33 GMT</pubDate>
